    "claim": "Repayment, buyback, auction settlement, and refinance only enforce collection equality, then overwrite `lien.tokenId` with a caller-chosen `tokenId`. The protocol therefore treats all NFTs in a collection as fungible and never requires returning the originally supplied NFT.",
    "impact": "A borrower can take a high-value or rare NFT, then close the loan with any cheaper token from the same collection. The lender receives a materially worse asset and loses the rarity premium, which can represent most of the NFT's value.",
    "paths": [
