      "Borrower later calls `repayWithNft` with a cheap floor token from the same collection, or uses `buyNftFromMarket` / `auctionSellNft` to settle with an arbitrary replacement token.",
      "The lien is rewritten to the cheaper token ID and the lender can only withdraw that substitute NFT."
    ]
